snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: The Hunters Song [SNES] Romhack
snippet.description:
The Legend of Zelda: The Hunters Song
Hack of The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past
Hack Released by Alfonsodelavega, Zscream
v1 https://romhackplaza.org/romhacks/the-legend-of-zelda-the-hunters-song-snes/
Release date: 2024

"Old Man Link is visited by an old acquaintance, but what has precipitated this visit? Why, another adventure, of course... But why, indeed?"
